wsdl:operation.name: GetSitesXml
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given an array of site numbers, this method returns the site metadata for each one. Send the array of site codes in this format: 'NetworkName:SiteCode'

wsdl:operation.name: GetSiteInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given a site number, this method returns the site's metadata. Send the site code in this format: 'NetworkName:SiteCode'

wsdl:operation.name: GetVariableInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given a variable code, this method returns the variable's name. Pass in the variable in this format: 'NetworkName:Variable'

wsdl:operation.name: GetSites
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given an array of site numbers, this method returns the site metadata for each one. Send the array of site codes in this format: 'NetworkName:SiteCode'

wsdl:operation.name: GetSiteInfoObject
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given a site number, this method returns the site's metadata. Send the site code in this format: 'NetworkName:SiteCode'

wsdl:operation.name: GetVariableInfoObject
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given a variable code, this method returns the variable's siteName. Pass in the variable in this format: 'NetworkName:Variable'

wsdl:operation.name: GetValues
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Given a site number, a variable, a start date, and an end date, this method returns a time series. Pass in the sitecode and variable in this format: 'NetworkName:SiteCode' and 'NetworkName:Variable'
